  "description": "A few days ago, we gifted a NOTRED tee and the Memento Mori ring to Oddible. \n\nNo plan behind it. Just felt right in the moment to gift it to a fellow grinder who’s work is steadily building a reputation within the global techno underground circuit.\n\nThen last night at Gylt, somewhere between the red lights and that heavy, rolling bass… We noticed it.\n\nSame tee. \nSame ring. \nJust… living its own life out there.\n\nYou don’t really control where what you create ends up. You just keep creating—and hope it finds the right rooms, the right people, the right nights.\nThis one found its place.\n.\n#NOTRED #Oddible #GyltBangalor #techno #brand",
